OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781880484
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to return to Westminster
OL,4,Cafter by-election win
OL,6,FAndy Burnham will make his return to
OL,7,FWestminster after winning the
OL,8,FMakerfield by-election.
OL,10,FThe Mayor of Greater Manchester swept
OL,11,Fto victory as he held on to the Labour
OL,12,Fstronghold with a majority of 9231.
OL,14,FIn his victory speech, Andy Burnham
OL,15,Fsaid: "Everyone knows that politics
OL,16,Fisn't working.
OL,18,F"Everyone can feel that the country
OL,19,Fisn't where it should be. Tonight
OL,20,Fcould, just could, be the turning
OL,21,Fpoint.
OL,26,@wD@GOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781880484
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to return to Westminster
OL,4,Cafter by-election win
OL,6,F"From here on I will give everything I
OL,7,Fhave got to make it so. To ensure the
OL,8,Fname Makerfield is forever synonymous
OL,9,Fwith bringing about the change this
OL,10,Fcountry needs."
OL,12,FHe added: "I am proud that this place
OL,13,Fhas shone in the world's spotlight for
OL,14,Fthe last few weeks, and the warmth,
OL,15,Fhumour and hospitality of its people
OL,16,Fhas been on show for all to see. It
OL,17,Fwill never be a stepping stone to me,
OL,18,Fbut instead will be my touchstone.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@OO]tD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781880484
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to return to Westminster
OL,4,Cafter by-election win
OL,6,F"A Makerfield test at the heart of
OL,7,FBritish politics will make sure that
OL,8,Fthe places Westminster has neglected
OL,9,Fwill now get fairness."
OL,11,FAndy Burnham left the count almost
OL,12,Fimmediately after his speech.
OL,14,FAs he got into a car with his wife and
OL,15,Fdaughter, he said he was going for a
OL,16,F"pint".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@WO]xD@AOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
