PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781880484
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to return to Westminster
OL,4,Cafter by-election win
OL,6,FHe told ITV News during the campaign:
OL,7,F"This is a change by-election, and if
OL,8,Fpeople do put their trust in me I will
OL,9,Fchange politics and I will give this
OL,10,Fplace more power and influence than it
OL,11,Fhad before."
OL,13,FDespite his popularity as the Mayor of
OL,14,FGreater Manchester, Burnham faced
OL,15,Fcriticism from other parties for using
OL,16,FMakerfield as a "stepping stone" to
OL,17,Fthe top job of Labour leader and prime
OL,18,Fminister.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781880484
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to return to Westminster
OL,4,Cafter by-election win
OL,6,FBurnham hit back at these claims
OL,7,Fsaying it was "a strange stepping
OL,8,Fstone that brings you back to where
OL,9,Fyou started 25 years ago", referencing
OL,10,Fhis previous position as the MP for
OL,11,Fneighbouring constituency Leigh.
OL,13,FDespite this, he has acknowledged he
OL,14,Fwould put himself forward to replace
OL,15,FSir Keir Starmer in any leadership
OL,16,Fcontest and has long been touted as
OL,17,Fthe likely winner of any race.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
