PN,36606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781880484
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to return to Westminster
OL,4,Cafter by-election win
OL,6,FPolling has shown Burnham to be the
OL,7,Fmost popular Labour politician in the
OL,8,Fcountry, with only his lack of a
OL,9,FWestminster seat barring him from
OL,10,Fchallenging the prime minister.
OL,12,FThe by-election was triggered by the
OL,13,Fresignation of former Labour
OL,14,FMakerfield MP Josh Simons, who stood
OL,15,Fdown to pave the way for the Greater
OL,16,FManchester Mayor to return to
OL,17,FWestminster.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
