PN,36607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781880484
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to return to Westminster
OL,4,Cafter by-election win
OL,6,FThe vote was touted as a race between
OL,7,FMr Burnham and Reform UK candidate
OL,8,FRobert Kenyon, with the former arguing
OL,9,Fthe by-election would prove he could
OL,10,Fwin back voters who now support Reform.
OL,12,FReform UK's leader Nigel Farage
OL,13,Fclaimed the by-election was "the
OL,14,Fbiggest in half a century" with the
OL,15,Ffight between the two candidates being
OL,16,Fa "David vs Goliath battle".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
