PN,36608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781880484
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to return to Westminster
OL,4,Cafter by-election win
OL,6,FReform UK's loss will throw into
OL,7,Fquestion their future potential in the
OL,8,FNorth West, having now lost two by-
OL,9,Felections in a row following their
OL,10,Fdefeat to the Greens in another
OL,11,FGreater Manchester seat, Gorton and
OL,12,FDenton.
OL,14,FDespite their loss Mr Kenyon did see a
OL,15,Fsignificant increase in his share of
OL,16,Fthe vote, having secured just 18% in
OL,17,Fthe 2024 General Election where he
OL,18,Falso stood as Reform UK's candidate.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
