PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781880484
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to return to Westminster
OL,4,Cafter by-election win
OL,6,FWhile Makerfield has long been
OL,7,Fconsidered a Labour stronghold, recent
OL,8,Felections threw Mr Burnham's chances
OL,9,Fof winning the seat into doubt.
OL,11,FCabinet minister Lisa Nandy said it
OL,12,Fwas "history in the making" after Andy
OL,13,FBurnham won the Makerfield by-election.
OL,26,@tD@EOUtD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
