PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781880484
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to return to Westminster
OL,4,Cafter by-election win
OL,6,FIn Wigan, which includes part of
OL,7,FMakerfield, Labour lost all 22 of its
OL,8,Fcouncillors in the May local
OL,9,Felections, with Reform picking up 24
OL,10,Fof the 25 seats up for grabs.
OL,12,FIn the eight Makerfield wards that
OL,13,Fvoted in the local election, Reform
OL,14,Fsecured 50% of the vote while Labour
OL,15,Fgot 23%.
OL,17,FWith Mr Burnham likely to make his
OL,18,Freturn to Westminster on Monday, focus
OL,19,Fwill quickly shift to whether he will
OL,20,Fchallenge Sir Keir in a leadership
OL,21,Fcontest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
