PN,36612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781880484
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to return to Westminster
OL,4,Cafter by-election win
OL,6,FHis victory also means he must resign
OL,7,Fas the Mayor of Greater Manchester,
OL,8,Ftriggering a Mayoral election which
OL,9,FReform UK and the Green Party will be
OL,10,Fkeen to seize from Labour.
OL,12,FIt is understood one of the Deputy
OL,13,FMayors, Paul Dennett or Kate Green,
OL,14,Fwill take over as the interim Mayor of
OL,15,FGreater Manchester until an election
OL,16,Fis held.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
