PN,36613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781880484
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to return to Westminster
OL,4,Cafter by-election win
OL,6,FThe former Health Secretary Wes
OL,7,FStreeting has made it clear he would
OL,8,Frun in any leadership contest, while
OL,9,Fformer Deputy Prime Minister Angela
OL,10,FRayner and Environment Secretary Ed
OL,11,FMiliband have also indicated they
OL,12,Fcould enter the race.
OL,14,FThe declaration came just after 3am on
OL,15,FFriday 19 June, in which he received
OL,16,F24,927 votes. The turnout was the
OL,17,Fhighest in a parliamentary by-election
OL,18,Fin nearly seven years at 58.75%.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/14
